      What’s Skip Tracing ?

      Already have your data, but lists are incomplete? Our skip-trace append is the fastest way to complete your lead list with data that moves your business forward. We warehouse over 175MM landlines, 250MM cell phones and 150MM email addresses to fill in the gaps on your lead lists with the highest quality homeowner information.

      Download Sample List Now
      • Data updated daily
      • Only pay for matches
      • Up to 10 cell phone numbers, 2 land lines, & Email
      • Typical Turnaround of 24 hours or less

      Flexible Pricing

      ​ “Eddie took care of me on correcting a stack list that wasn’t correct. He provided excellent customer service, I ended up purchasing another 300 leads and now I understand how to build the stacks myself. Thank you again.”

      Justin Lee

      ​ “I really like their data so far. I was new and didn’t know how to stack my list in the best way and Dom reached out to me and helped me build a list that was best to land a deal. Data and customer service is great, I will continue to work with them and look out for their new features in the future!”

      Antone Grae

Very professional team and they provide the leads on time as what they promised. You can never go wrong with Geopoint Data thats for sure.”

      Magan Fatah

      ​ ​ ​ “Their customer support is top notch. Eddie solved my issues in a very helpful and patient manner. Definitely would recommend!”

      Vivenli Go

      ​“Another investor recommended Geopoint Data and I have never been so happy! The quality of the data is fantastic and the customer service was excellent! The patience that they had answering newbie questions was great! Thank you so much guys!”

      FAQ’s

      What is skip tracing?
      Skip trace is the process of finding a homeowner’s contact information by referencing data we already have: Name, Property or Mailing Address. We help Realtors, Investors & Wholesalers find phone numbers and emails of people on their lead list.
      How long will it take?
      We’ll have your completed lead list ready within 24 hours of completed payment.
      What information do I need on someone for Skip Tracing to work?
      You will need their full name & address. With that information we’ll help you find their phone number and email.
      Can you skip trace LLCs and other businesses?
      Yes, you can skip trace LLCs. The process is the same.

      Get started with Real Estate Leads using Predictive Data

      Get Target Leads! Start Skip Tracing
